casebody.data:
Robert BIROS, petitioner,
v.
Kathleen KANE, Attorney General of Pennsylvania, et al. No. 15-910. Supreme Court of the United States May 2, 2016.

Motion of respondents for leave to file a brief in opposition under seal granted. Motion of petitioner for leave to file a reply brief under seal granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Common *1824Pleas of Pennsylvania, Allegheny County denied.
